#Tokyo2020 #Olympics

node.text:
Hannah Walker @spannawalker previews the Tokyo 2020 Olympic Games with Rebecca Charlton, Anna Buick, Bart de Jong and Miriam Welte, talking about the 5 cycling disciplines ahead of competition getting underway, tomorrow, Saturday 24th July! 

#Tokyo2020 #Olympics

May be an image of 1 person, bicycle and text that says '東 05008 京 CASOCO REFUG TEAN TEAM Orla Chennaoui @SportsOrla Masomah Ali Zada, an Afghan refugee living in France, just completed her first ever time trial, and it was at the Olympics. She just told me she wants to send a message to all the girls back home who' re told they can ride a bike, that anything is possible. What a woman.'.
